	<ThingDef ParentName="KOTOR_KinrathBase">
		<defName>KOTOR_Kinrath</defName>
		<label>Kinrath</label>
		<description>Kinrath are species of large, non-sentient arachnoids found on Dantooine and Kashyyyk. They have four legs and a leg-like, poisonous appendage coming out of their faces that they use to attack prey or other perceived enemies. Kinrath are blind but can sense heat which allowed them to navigate their way around and identify potential threats. They identified members of their own hive using a specialized sweat gland in the abdomen which excreted a specific scent.</description>
		<statBases>
			<MoveSpeed>5</MoveSpeed>
			<ArmorRating_Blunt>0.35</ArmorRating_Blunt>
			<ArmorRating_Sharp>0.12</ArmorRating_Sharp>
			<ComfyTemperatureMin>0</ComfyTemperatureMin>
			<MarketValue>100</MarketValue>
			<LeatherAmount>0</LeatherAmount>
		</statBases>
	</ThingDef>
	
